home.entry: I hope that one day this site will be useful.
home.about: Translated by Google. I quickly edited the skeleton of my personal project so that I could write it all down somewhere. So sorry that it plays with all colors. I have no restrictions here (e.g. text length, ..) and I can write it as I want. I believe that I still have a lot of traveling ahead of me, so it is already possible to accumulate it somewhere. In parallel, I sometimes expand my stuff here, so why not link it. It takes a while, there's a lot. Many experiences, work, writing, activities, ..
